    'name' => 'text_haiku_to_emoji',
    'description' => 'Convert a haiku poem into an emoji art visualization. Each line of the haiku is rendered alongside a sentiment-based emoji bar and season emoji. Combines text_haiku_generator, text_sentiment_analysis, and emoji_art_renderer concepts. Pure function, no side effects.',
    'parameters' => 
